serves: 65
---
6500 g pasta
300 g pasta gluten free

3250 g peas canned
1.5 kg cucumber
1.5 kg bell pepper
1 kg celery
2 kg carrot
500 g avocado
975 g tomatoes dried
780 ml olive oil
390 ml vinegar balsamic
195 ml syrup
390 ml lemon juice
390 gram parsley
---
# Instructions
- Cook the pasta according to the instructions. Cook GF pasta as well.
- Meanwhile, whisk the ingredients for the dressing. When the pasta is done and
drained, mix it with the dressing. Make sure that it can cool down.
- Chop all veggies the same size (small), chop the parsley
- Add salt and pepper according to taste
- Mix everything and serve